When Lu Yi came into the room, Steward Zhang closed the door and went back. Lu Yi stepped forward and bowed to the ground. "My nephew Lu Yi has seen uncle Li Qun.



"Yi 'er, it's you! I heard zhang Yang said that the mountain down a zhuozhou people's Lu Yi, feel strange, did not think it is really you this child nonsense. Didn't you go into the mountains with jin Dongzi's uncle? Why are you here?"



Originally, the current master of the book hall, is the zhuozhou city chief Li Qun, the master of yulinzi's younger brother Yufengzi apprentice, after one hundred years of accession to the wto, replaced by Lu Feng, after returning to the mountain, to give the name of wood fengzi, all who return to the mountain, can be given the name of the law to show reward, but also really become yaoshan backbone. Li Qun returned to Shanmen, but his family was still in Zhuozhou, so he went back to visit them many times, so he was very familiar with Lu Yi's family.
